</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_62" id="31r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_62_r1l8">Den von Erffurt </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_62_r1l9"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt / wıe eẅch hanns von Saluelt vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_62_r1l10"><expan>Günth<ex>er</ex></expan> von <expan>Herbıſlawbe<ex>n</ex></expan> eẅr <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>kündıgt</expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / vvıe daʒ dıe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_62_r1l11"><expan>ʒeychenmeıſt<ex>er</ex></expan> der <expan>wollenweb<ex>er</ex></expan> bey vns Jrem <expan>dıen<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>botten</expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_62_r1l12">niht geſtatten <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Jren weyt ʒe füren etc das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_62_r1l13"><expan>v<ex>er</ex>nom<ex>en</ex></expan> . Vnd laſſen eẅr <expan>fürſıchtık<ex>eit</ex></expan> <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> / daʒ wır dıe <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> ʒeychen = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_62_r1l14"><expan>meıſt<ex>er</ex></expan> bey vns beſant vnd <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ʒu rede geſacʒt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . dıe <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_62_r1l15">vns <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> / waʒ dıe <expan>obg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> eẅr <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> vnd Jr <expan>dıen<ex>er</ex></expan> dıe ſache </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_62_r1l16">mıt dem weyt bey vns <expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>gehalt<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd gehandelt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / denn </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_62_r1l17">ſölıch ſache vormals bey vns gehandelt vnd <expan>gehalt<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>worde<ex>n</ex></expan> ſein </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_62_r1l18">vvıe <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ſo <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır doch vmb <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>wıll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> beſtellet daʒ <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_62_r1l19"><expan>B<ex>urgern</ex></expan> gegünnet ıſt Jren weyt nuʒemal ʒe füren als Jr denn <expan>beg<ex>er</ex>t</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_62_r1l20">habt . <expan>Daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> <expan>bıtt<ex>en</ex></expan> wır eẅr <expan>weıſh<ex>eit</ex></expan> mıt <expan>gancʒe<ex>m</ex></expan> fleıſʒ . Jr wellt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_62_r1l21">mıt <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>burg<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vnd den <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>ſchık<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd <expan>beſtell<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / daʒ ſıe Jr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_62_r1l22">ſache bey vns fürbas handeln vnd halten als denn bey vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_62_r1l23"><expan>herkome<ex>n</ex></expan> ıſt . VVan wır <expan>vng<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>hengen</expan> <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>geſtatte<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>wolt<ex>en</ex></expan> daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_62_r1l24">kein Neẅekeıt bey vns an ſıe gelegt wurd . / Vnd wa wır </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_62_r1l25"><expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erſamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc . <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> vt <expan>ſ<ex>upra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_62" id="31r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Den von Erffurt </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt, wie ewch Hanns von Salvelt und
                                <expan>Günth<ex>er</ex></expan> von
                            <expan>Herbislawbe<ex>n</ex></expan>, ewr
                        <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan>, <expan>v<ex>er</ex>kündigt</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n,</expan> wie daz die
                            <expan>zeychenmeist<ex>er</ex></expan> der
                            <expan>wollenweb<ex>er</ex></expan> bey uns irem
                            <expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>botten</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und niht gestatten
                            <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, iren weyt ze füren etc., das
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nom<ex>en</ex></expan> und lassen ewr
                                <expan>fürsichtik<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz wir die
                            <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
                            zeychen<expan>meist<ex>er</ex></expan> bey uns besant und
                                <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> zu rede gesaczt
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Die <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> uns
                                <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>, waz die
                                <expan>obg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> ewr
                            <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> und ir <expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> die
                        sache mit dem weyt bey uns <expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>gehalt<ex>en</ex></expan> und gehandelt
                        <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, denn sölich sache vormals bey uns gehandelt
                        und <expan>gehalt<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>worde<ex>n</ex></expan> sein; wie <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> so
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir doch umb
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>will<ex>e</ex>n</expan> bestellet, daz <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urgern</ex></expan> gegünnet ist, iren weyt nuzemal ze füren,
                        als ir denn <expan>beg<ex>er</ex>t</expan> habt.
                            <expan>Daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> wir ewr <expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan> mit
                                <expan>gancze<ex>m</ex></expan> fleisz, ir wellt mit
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>n</expan> und den <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan> und <expan>bestell<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, daz
                        sie ir sache bey uns fürbas handeln und halten, als denn bey uns
                                <expan>herkome<ex>n</ex></expan> ist, wan wir
                            <expan>ung<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>hengen</expan>
<expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gestatte<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>wolt<ex>en,</ex></expan> daz kein newekeit bey uns an sie gelegt
                        wurd. Und wa wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
